                        <interp inst="t18440101-name-318" type="given" value="DENNIS"></interp>DENNIS KEYS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic"> police-constable D</hi> 113.) I produce a certificate of John<lb></lb>son's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person—I was present at the trial.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440101-name-319" type="witnessName">
