                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 69.) I produce a certificate of Collins' former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—Col<lb></lb>lins is the person—I was present at the trial.</p>
